text: Vélizy-Villacoublay is a French commune. It is in the southwestern suburbs of Paris 13.9 km (8.6 mi) from the center and 3.2 km (2.0 mi) east of Versailles. About 20,030 people lived here in 2006. == Education == * Institut des sciences et techniques des Yvelines * Université de Versailles Saint-Quentin- en-Yvelines Category:Communes in Yvelines
